Hello. Thank you for visiting. This page talks a bit about me. I am passionate about:

Entrepreneurship. All Things Tech. Software. Data. Gadgets. Networking. Events. Music. Reading Anything. [Writing](https://medium.com/@GINAQ). Traveling. Photography. [Philanthropy](https://syncderella.github.io/causes). Food. Healthy Eating - check out my page [HealthyCulinares](http://www.facebook.com/HealthyCulinaires). Fitness. Running. Being A Geek Mom. Being A [Global Citizen](http://www.globalcitizen.net).

You can also find me on [Medium](https://medium.com/@GINAQ) | [LinkedIn](http://www.linkedin.com/in/ginaqvu) | [Facebook](http://www.facebook.com/ginaqvu) | [StackExchange](http://stackexchange.com/users/7357701/gina-q)
